race.comment: INSTEAD (4) did a good job last start to finish third at Narromine over 1600m. Cherry-ripe now and well placed with the claim. BROADCAST BOOGIE (6) struggled to see the trip out when a fading seventh over 2000m at Mudgee. Proven at this trip and Weir sticks. Each way player. KIRK (3) is holding his form this time in and stays in the mix after running fourth over this trip at Narromine. Respect. EVEN MILE MISSILE (1) hasn't been far away lately and steps up to the mile for the first time today. Charged late when a narrow head second over 1300m at this track. Izzy Neale rides again with the claim and deserves respect.
